== English ==
===Etymology===
By analogy with [[software]] et al.

=== Noun ===
'''bloatware'''

# [[software|Software]] that that is overpacked with features (a result of [[featureitis]]) and therefore slow or [[unwieldy]]; software that occupies an excessive amount of [[memory]].

